      "description": "Beth-Emily employs a 'peaceful minimalist' style, characterized by a muted, earthy color palette and a soft, understated typographic approach. The design emphasizes natural textures and subtle visual cues, allowing brand imagery and content to take precedence. Surfaces are generally light, with interaction points highlighted by gentle washes of color and a distinct lack of heavy shadows, conveying an organic and approachable feel.",
